channel.title: A little instrumental song I made.
channel.description:
Yeah, had an afternoon with nothing to do, and this is what came of it. It's Holiday Road originally sung by Lindsay Buckingham, and I made an instrumental out of some midi file I found on the Internet. Enjoy!
[url='https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7i53i3Tyzgw']https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7i53i3Tyzgw[/url]
Yeah, a rookie attempt at Magix Music Maker, I know.:retard:
